    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "This college infrastructure is huge and good. Our classroom were provided with Air conditioning service. And it also has 2 auditorium. Also good food provided on canteens. There are two library and a study hall so there is lots of space to study.",
