          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Our class had a ratio of boys and girls about 60% boys and 40% girls.",
          "name": "Siddhesh Pattipaka",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "It also conducted Industrial visits, our first visit was at Manali for 9 days and second was at Himachal Pradesh for 10 days.",
          "name": "Siddhesh Pattipaka",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Rhythm. It’s a cultural fest that this college hosts and it is the only time of the year where there’s a vast majority of events you could participate in.",
