        },
        {
          "text": "TECHITHON. It’s a Tech fest that this college hosts and it has tech events which encourages students to grow and learn more as this aligns with our course.",
          "name": "Review Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "A ground to play and exercise, for sports such as cricket, football, volleyball etc.",
